paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
select productName,pogId,orders from (
    select  b.productName, b.pogId, count(distinct a.subOrderId) as orders,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY count(distinct a.subOrderId) DESC) AS rn
    from `temp.attri_Orders` a left join `all(agCmDump)` b on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId 
    where DATEDIFF(CURRENT_DATE(),a.orderDate) BETWEEN 1 AND 30
    and a.Channel = 'SEO'
    group by b.productName, b.pogId
    order by orders desc) 
where rn<104
",1000)
